Matrix3 Class

Extends AbstractMatrix
Defined in: src/davinci-eight/math/Matrix3.ts:24
Module: math
Parent Module: EIGHT

3x3 (square) matrix of numbers. Constructs a Matrix3 by wrapping a Float32Array. The elements are stored in column-major order: 0 3 6 1 4 7 2 5 8
